songs.title: Not The Same*
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: 2 Chainz]
Me to call, buckle in
The cause and effect, the lost cause stress
I'm playin' right now, y'all call next
Ye ain't never ball, triple 0 baggings
Use my scale so much that bitch need new batteries

[Chorus: Ne-Yo]
I'm not the same, I'm not the same, not the same
